value: 6324 - Hospital and Medical Service Plans Summary > HEALTH CARE INSURANCE LTD. (formerly APPM COUNCIL HEALTH BENEFITS LTD.) is an Australian public company. Its operations cover accident and health insurance. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. HEALTH CARE INSURANCE LTD. is headquartered in Burnie, Tasmania. It is headed by director Carolyn Ann Harris. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $30.72 million. Its net profit totalled $4.22 million. HEALTH CARE INSURANCE LTD. forms part of the finance, insurance, and real estate industry sector. Key Personnel > No key personnel were found for the selected company.
